<!DOCTYPE qhelp PUBLIC
  "-//Semmle//qhelp//EN"
  "qhelp.dtd">
<qhelp>
<overview>
<p>This query finds crypto variables initialized using weak randomness like process IDs or timestamps.</p>

<p>Limitations: the query does not track weak randomness through a hash function, so keys derived by hashing a weak source are not flagged.</p>
</overview>
</qhelp>
